{
  "id": "69dc0834e96e947c659da176",
  "title": "リンクは道路、ページは交差点",
  "created": 1776027703,
  "updated": 1776028800,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "69dc0834e96e947c659da176",
      "text": "リンクは道路、ページは交差点",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027703,
      "updated": 1776027703
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0876000000000062c6da",
      "text": "道路の[メタファ]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027766,
      "updated": 1776027910
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0837000000000062c6d6",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027703,
      "updated": 1776027703
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc089b000000000062c6db",
      "text": "ページが交差点として機能するには、4つのリンクが必要",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027803,
      "updated": 1776027876
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc08e4000000000062c6dc",
      "text": "　1. 来た道",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027876,
      "updated": 1776027963
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0919000000000062c6df",
      "text": "　2. 直進",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027931,
      "updated": 1776027961
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0924000000000062c6e0",
      "text": "　3. 右折",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027940,
      "updated": 1776027976
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc094c000000000062c6e1",
      "text": "　4. 左折",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027981,
      "updated": 1776027990
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0909000000000062c6dd",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027913,
      "updated": 1776027913
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc09ba000000000062c6e2",
      "text": "リンクが3つなら、行先を選択できる",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028090,
      "updated": 1776028170
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0a0a000000000062c6e3",
      "text": "Y 字路のイメージ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028171,
      "updated": 1776028197
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0909000000000062c6de",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027913,
      "updated": 1776027913
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0a3c000000000062c6e6",
      "text": "リンクが2つなら、行くか戻るかの選択肢しかない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028220,
      "updated": 1776028273
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0a71000000000062c6e7",
      "text": "橋のイメージ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028274,
      "updated": 1776028288
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0a85000000000062c6e8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028293,
      "updated": 1776028293
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0a85000000000062c6e9",
      "text": "リンクがひとつなら、そのひとつの道を進むしかないし、",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028293,
      "updated": 1776028377
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0ad9000000000062c6ea",
      "text": "その道が来た道なら、もう先へは進めない",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028377,
      "updated": 1776028425
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0b16000000000062c6eb",
      "text": "袋小路のイメージ",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028438,
      "updated": 1776028454
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0a27000000000062c6e5",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776028199,
      "updated": 1776028199
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0841000000000062c6d9",
      "text": "[橋を架ける]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027713,
      "updated": 1776027735
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0838000000000062c6d7",
      "text": "[赤リンクは行き止まり]",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027704,
      "updated": 1776027709
    },
    {
      "id": "69dc0839000000000062c6d8",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "5b5e7121417cf700145b98c2",
      "created": 1776027705,
      "updated": 1776027705
    }
  ]
}